    "(5) Scalability and adaptability: Scaling AI solutions to handle large volumes of data and adapt to changing conditions can be challenging [243].",
    "As food safety needs evolve and data volumes increase, AI systems must be capable of scaling up and adapting to new types of data and scenarios.",
    "6) Regulatory compliance and data privacy: Ensuring that AI systems comply with food safety regulations and data privacy laws is a significant challenge.",
    "Compliance with regulations such as the FDA's Food Safety Modernization Act (FSMA) and data protection laws requires careful consideration of AI system design and data handling practices [244].",
